@baseUrl = http://localhost:8084
@jwt = PEGA_AQUI_TU_JWT_REAKTOR

### Obtener configuración de refresh del usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/configuracion-refresh-redes
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Guardar configuración de refresh del usuario autenticado
PUT {{baseUrl}}/configuracion-refresh-redes
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autoRefresh": true,
  "refreshInterval": 15
}

### Desactivar auto refresh
PUT {{baseUrl}}/configuracion-refresh-redes
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autoRefresh": false,
  "refreshInterval": 30
}
